Viola. Aku Viola.

652
00:49:24,071 --> 00:49:27,491
- Suara tinggi.
- Viola.

653
00:49:30,076 --> 00:49:32,412
Mundur!

654
00:49:33,913 --> 00:49:37,333
Manchee. Spackle.

655
00:49:37,417 --> 00:49:39,127
Apa itu tadi?

656
00:49:39,210 --> 00:49:41,045
Itu desa Spackle.

657
00:49:47,760 --> 00:49:49,553
Merunduk!

658
00:49:51,722 --> 00:49:53,474
Bertarunglah. Jadi pria sejati.

659
00:49:53,557 --> 00:49:55,309
Fokus. Kendalikan Suara-mu.
Mereka membunuh ibuku.

660
00:49:55,392 --> 00:49:57,185
Berhenti! Jadi pria sejati.
Kendalikan Suara-mu.

661
00:49:57,269 --> 00:49:59,312
Mereka membunuh
ibuku. Todd, berhenti! Diam!

662
00:49:59,396 --> 00:50:01,314
- Diam.
